api_list.name: Get tracking job result
api_list.description: After you submit a video for processing, the "status" key will go from "queued" to "processing" to "completed". You can make a GET request, as shown on the right, to check for updates on the status of your tracking job
api_list.code:
import requests

url = "https://object-tracking.p.rapidapi.com/job/66037ab7-01c3-42bb-a49f-8076020a7f1b"

headers = {
            "X-RapidAPI-Key": "SIGN-UP-FOR-KEY",
            "X-RapidAPI-Host": "object-tracking.p.rapidapi.com"
        }

response = requests.get(url, headers=headers)
print(response.json())
